<a href="http://sites.google.com/site/jarhmanderhome/MySong_LO.nsf?attredirects=0" class="postlink">This little demo</a> features a unique effect that I have never seen in any NSF: basically when I play a bass sample, I have two parts, the beginning and the loop, and they play in one shot. Looping correctly a sample is pretty difficult due to the way the DMC loops... Also I'm using writes to $4011 to enhance a bit the drum.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=336">Jarhmander</a> — Sun Aug 15, 2010 8:30 pm</p><hr />
